Steve Hultay wrote:
&gt;  Nellie,
&gt;
&gt;  That one file &quot;What are you to me?&quot; A man answers clearly i believe
&gt;  says &quot;Nothing&quot;. That is a real EVP, probably a class A and that did
&gt;  not come from the box.

It must be a Class B, then, as I am hearing &quot;husband&quot;.  That fits with 
the other one where he says I&#39;m his wife.  He has been trying to 
convince me for over a year that I am the reincarnation of his long dead 
spouse, so I was quite intrigued to get these as some of the results 
from my very first day trying ITC work.

&gt;  That was spoken directly into your recorder. I
&gt;  get them on occasion, i feel that only happens with a grounded spirit
&gt;  in a location and is confused by the box....Maybe (I don&#39;t Know) It
&gt;  sounds somewhat logical though.

Or it could just be that I have been nagging him to hear his voice.  
Like I said, I&#39;d never managed to get even one evp out of him in 15 
months of trying.  He&#39;s pretty clever, so I couldn&#39;t imagine that he 
couldn&#39;t figure out how to.  The sense I was getting from him was that 
since he was shot through the throat during the Civil War, he was 
concerned that he would sound scary if I ever heard him.  It actually 
means a lot to me that he finally let me hear him in his own voice.  I 
guess he now trusts me not to freak out.  As if I ever did.

&gt;  Anyway, Great Files and welcome to the group !!!

Thanks!  Actually, it was your site that convinced me to break down and 
give ITC work a try.


Nellie


